1. *Kratak* roman je lako pročitati. (A *short* novel is easy to read.)
2. Treba nam *kratka* pauza da odmorimo mozak. (We need a *short* break to rest our brains.)
3. Danas imamo *kratak* sastanak u 14 sati. (Today we have a *brief* meeting at 2 pm.)
4. *Kratki* pregled knjige je dostupan na internetu. (A *brief* book review is available online.)
5. Ovo je *kratak* spoj, moramo ga popraviti. (This is a *short* circuit, we need to fix it.)
6. *Kratka* kosa joj odlično stoji. (She looks great with *short* hair.)
7. Predavanje je bilo *kratko* i jasno. (The lecture was *short* and clear.)
8. Moramo biti *kratkoročni* i dugoročni ciljevi. (We need to have *short-term* and long-term goals.)
9. Njen odgovor bio je *kratak* i jasan. (Her response was *brief* and clear.)
10. Sinoć smo imali *kratku* šetnju gradom. (Last night we had a *short* walk around the city.)